---
title: Mozzarella and Pesto Crusted Chicken with Roasted Potatoes and Green Salad
description: Pesto is the secret ingredient in this recipe! It not only adds delicious flavor to the chicken, but also acts as the glue for a crunchy panko coating. Crispy roasted potatoes and a light green salad complete this easy weeknight dinner.
